    "title": "Tata CLiQ is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Tata CLiQ. We are on the lookout for a dedicated E-commerce Executive to strengthen our Gurgaon-based team.\n\nAbout Tata CLiQ:\nTata CLiQ is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata CLiQ!",
